    "has_children": false,
    "archived": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Within two weeks, Chen trapped 20 cats and had them sterilized. The males were returned to the garden near the building the next day, while the females typically needed 2-3 days to recover at the clinic. In addition to the sterilization costs, some cats also required medical treatment. Though the animal hospital offered discounts for strays, it has been a significant expense for Chen, who initially covered 20,000 RMB (about $3,000 USD) herself before fundraising online, to which I also contributed.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Within two weeks, Chen trapped 20 cats and had them sterilized. The males were returned to the garden near the building the next day, while the females typically needed 2-3 days to recover at the clinic. In addition to the sterilization costs, some cats also required medical treatment. Though the animal hospital offered discounts for strays, it has been a significant expense for Chen, who initially covered 20,000 RMB (about $3,000 USD) herself before fundraising online, to which I also contributed.",
