    "has_children": false,
    "archived": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Chen shared her fundraising strategies with me. She carefully researches crowdfunding platforms to run successful campaigns. She also started an online group and invites anyone she sees feeding the cats to join. Chen has done a lot of research into effective TNR programs in other areas.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Chen shared her fundraising strategies with me. She carefully researches crowdfunding platforms to run successful campaigns. She also started an online group and invites anyone she sees feeding the cats to join. Chen has done a lot of research into effective TNR programs in other areas.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "id": "1b30d7c4-4475-8075-a1fe-c788996158c4",
    "parent": {
      "type": "page_id",
      "page_id": "1b20d7c4-4475-80e1-bc3e-dd737b67db2c"
    },
    "created_time": "2025-03-11T06:28:00.000Z",
    "last_edited_time": "2025-03-11T06:29:00.000Z",
    "created_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "fa626e5b-d1fc-42ce-9394-3d5014e1bebd"
    },
    "last_edited_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "fa626e5b-d1fc-42ce-9394-3d5014e1bebd"
    },
    "has_children": false,
    "archived": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Chen works in investment banking and has been trying to get her well-off colleagues involved in TNR. At lunchtime, she sometimes helps her colleagues to clean up their used takeout containers, which she then repurposes as food and water bowls for the stray cats. She says she plans to more formally ask for her colleagues' help in the future, but for now, she hopes this gesture will notice them that she's actively working on something. Chen believes you have to provide a service before you can expect others to join your efforts.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Chen works in investment banking and has been trying to get her well-off colleagues involved in TNR. At lunchtime, she sometimes helps her colleagues to clean up their used takeout containers, which she then repurposes as food and water bowls for the stray cats. She says she plans to more formally ask for her colleagues' help in the future, but for now, she hopes this gesture will notice them that she's actively working on something. Chen believes you have to provide a service before you can expect others to join your efforts.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    }
  },
