        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Through our work, female cats in our community no longer have to endure the stress of repeated pregnancy, and the number of stray cats in our community has been brought under control. By addressing the root cause through sterilization, TNR provides a long-term, sustainable solution that is better for the cats and the neighborhood.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
